title: A homeless youth asked a stranger for food. The man responded with a question that changed the kid’s life forever
body_snippet: The man was alone and smartly dressed in a button-down shirt, khaki pants and professorial eyeglasses. He sauntered through the food stalls, oblivious to Mutabazi getting closer with each step. This guy doesn’t have a clue, Mutabazi, then 15, thought as he closed in on the man. Not once did he check over his shoulder or put his hand to his wallet to make sure it was there. Easy marks like this don’t come along very often. title: Sydney Sweeney and Lisa from Blackpink walk Emmys red carpet
body_snippet: Sydney Sweeney, Jenna Ortega, Selena Gomez and Lisa from Blackpink were among the stars walking the red carpet ahead of the Emmy Awards. The ceremony took place on Sunday at the Peacock Theatre in Los Angeles, rewarding the best TV shows of the past 12 months.

title: Attacking Qatar shows Israel doesn’t want a Gaza ceasefire
body_snippet: Netanyahu keeps changing his position on a Gaza ceasefire, using different ploys to keep the war going. For almost two years, Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu has gone out of his way to avoid agreeing to a Gaza ceasefire. In November 2023, a deal saw the release of 110 captives taken during Hamas’s October 7 attack on Israel. title: Оборонный банк проведет оценку Домодедово перед продажей
body_snippet: Промсвязьбанк (ПСБ) проведет комплексную оценку предприятий группы Домодедово перед его продажей, рассказали РБК два источника, знакомых с ходом подготовки к продаже актива. Один из них утверждает, что к работе привлечен также ВЭБ.РФ. Работа банков, по словам источников, должна быть завершена до декабря. «Важный рубеж — платеж Домодедово по облигациям, который назначен на декабрь.
